Introducing Mizuno's latest addition to their premium pant lineup, the Premier Pro Tapered Adult Baseball Pant. Designed for the modern athlete, this fitted baseball pant combines flexibility, durability, and style, making it an essential part of any player's wardrobe. Featuring a traditional tunnel-belt loop waist with a fly front and extended two-snap closure, these pants ensure a secure and comfortable fit. The double knee construction provides added protection, while the hemmed bottom and embroidered logo add a touch of sophistication. With set-in back pockets featuring button closures, these pants offer both functionality and a sleek, professional look on the field. table {
